<darktable_style version="1.0"><info><name>dehaze</name><description>Parameterized dehaze (#90 Bucket A.2). Lightroom-style Dehaze slider via darktable's hazeremoval module. Two axes: --param strength=V (-1.0 to 1.0; positive removes haze, negative adds atmospheric fog) and --param distance=V (0.0 to 1.0; depth-falloff range). Default strength=0.2 distance=0.2 (darktable defaults).</description></info><style><plugin><num>0</num><module>3</module><operation>hazeremoval</operation><op_params>cdcc4c3ecdcc4c3e0000000001000000</op_params><enabled>1</enabled><blendop_params>gz11eJxjYIAACQYYOOHEgAZY0QWAgBGLGANDgz0Ej1Q+dcF/IADRAGpyHQU=</blendop_params><blendop_version>14</blendop_version><multi_priority>0</multi_priority><multi_name></multi_name><multi_name_hand_edited>0</multi_name_hand_edited></plugin></style></darktable_style>
